      "duration": 1.04,
      "size": 16704,
      "text": "欢迎来到牛顿法实验。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.93,
      "size": 46944,
      "text": "如何求解方程f(x)=0？对于简单的方程，我们可以用代数方法。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.84,
      "size": 45504,
      "text": "但对于复杂的方程，比如x的五次方加x等于1，代数方法就无能为力了。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.56,
      "size": 24912,
      "text": "牛顿法提供了一种强大的数值求解方法。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-1",
      "filename": "concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.65,
      "size": 26352,
      "text": "牛顿法的核心思想是用切线来逼近曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-2",
      "filename": "concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.52,
      "size": 24336,
      "text": "从一个初始猜测开始，画出该点的切线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-3",
      "filename": "concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.56,
      "size": 24912,
      "text": "切线与x轴的交点就是下一个更好的近似。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-4",
      "filename": "concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.7,
      "size": 27216,
      "text": "重复这个过程，通常能快速收敛到真正的根。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "visualization",
      "line_id": "vis-1",
      "filename": "visualization-vis-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/visualization-vis-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.46,
      "size": 23328,
      "text": "让我们在图上观察牛顿法的迭代过程。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "visualization",
      "line_id": "vis-2",
      "filename": "visualization-vis-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/visualization-vis-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.53,
      "size": 24480,
      "text": "红点是当前的近似值，蓝线是该点的切线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "visualization",
      "line_id": "vis-3",
      "filename": "visualization-vis-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/visualization-vis-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.56,
      "size": 24912,
      "text": "切线与x轴的交点成为新的近似值。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "visualization",
      "line_id": "vis-4",
      "filename": "visualization-vis-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/visualization-vis-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.9,
      "size": 30384,
      "text": "注意每次迭代后，近似值如何快速接近真正的根。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "convergence",
      "line_id": "conv-1",
