      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/convergence-conv-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26784,
      "text": "牛顿法的收敛速度是二次的，非常快。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "convergence",
      "line_id": "conv-2",
